headline: 6,600 UNION PACIFIC TEAMSTERS RATIFY CONTRACT
summary: Thousands of maintenance of way workers at Union Pacific (UP) have voted to ratify a strong new contract. They are represented by the Brotherhood of Maintenance of Way Employes Division (BMWED) of the Teamsters Rail Conference.
